steps.html_instructions: Head east on E San Francisco St toward Cathedral Pl
Take the 1st left onto Old Santa Fe Trail
Turn right onto the Interstate 25 S ramp to Albuquerque
Take exit 242 for US-550 W/NM-165 E toward Rio Rancho/Placitas
Turn left onto US-64 BYP W/W Murray Dr

US-64 BYP W/W Murray Dr turns left and becomes US-64 W/W Main St
Continue to follow US-64 W

Slight left onto US-491 N/S Broadway (signs for I-491)
Continue to follow US-491 N
Entering Utah

Turn right onto US-191 N/N Main St
Continue to follow US-191 N
Take exit 157 to merge onto US-191 N/US-6 W toward Price/Salt Lake
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-15 N/Salt Lake City and merge onto I-15 N
